<li id="cite_note-23"><b><a href="#cite_ref-23" title="">^</a></b> see also: <a href="http://www.qudsdaily.com/archive/1384/html/2/1384-02-25/page2.html" class="external autonumber" title="http://www.qudsdaily.com/archive/1384/html/2/1384-02-25/page2.html" rel="nofollow">[3]</a></li>
